  Zr 0.329072 0.170928 0.500000
  Zr 0.170928 0.670928 0.841856
  Ir 0.750000 0.750000 0.000000
  Ir 0.250000 0.250000 0.000000
K_POINTS automatic
  24 24 24 0 0 0
